{"tid":2354643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧卡古：摩連奴調教簡尼同我當時一樣","createTime":"2021-01-05T15:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T09:28:49.000Z","uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7fe7d3b83897f08d536340a8115d875de3d382","tid":2354643,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"盧卡古：摩連奴調教簡尼同我當時一樣<br />\n2021-01-04 09:18:32<br />\n<br />\n比利時中鋒盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）表示，在摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）的調教下，哈利-簡尼（Harry Kane）被開發出了團隊屬性，變得更出色了，這就像當年摩帥對自己的指導一樣。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡古對比利時的《 Sport/Voetbal》雜誌說：「摩連奴教會我更好的為團隊效力，包括在壓迫逼搶和我的跑位方面。看看現在在熱刺，他在哈利-簡尼身上所做的。」<br />\n<br />\n在摩連奴手下，簡尼開發出了後撤進攻的踢法，今季英超中已經收穫了11次助攻。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡古還表示，自己這些年取得了很大進步，現在可以躋身世界前五名中鋒之列。<span class=\"red\">「過去五個月，我會把我放到世界前五名中鋒之列，我不想列出一份名單，但我認為自己在這個行列裡。」</span>"},{"pid":"b7486b5ca6b20edf063c46339c9fb78ff1b9fb21","tid":2354643,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"盧卡古：我是Top 5前鋒<br />\n2020年12月8日<br />\n<br />\n國際米蘭前鋒盧卡古表示，自己是現今球壇最強的5位前鋒之一。<br />\n<br />\n數起最強前鋒，你會想起那個球員？國際米蘭前鋒盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）今季意甲及歐聯上陣12場，共攻入13球及交出兩次助攻。他接受《法國足球》訪問時，直指自己是現今球壇最強的五位前鋒之一。 27歲的盧卡古說：「我是世界前五名的前鋒，如果基斯坦奴朗拿度、美斯及利雲度夫斯基可以突破自己，為什麼我做不到？」<span class=\"red\">他又在訪問中特別談到自己的優點，指「戰術上，於企位及走位上，我是不會出錯，永遠不會錯」。</span> 自上季盧卡古轉會國米後，這18個月他一直交出極高水準，於64場所有賽事共攻入46球，更為隊友交出了8次助攻，與其曼聯時低迷表現有極大出入，由2019年起計算，亦只有少數球員如C朗、美斯及利雲度夫斯基於入球可與他相比。"},{"pid":"5e35bb26c9eef1608c54ffd1ad109f2243e87f36","tid":2354643,"uid":67225,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.yqqlm.com/index/index/getInterUrl?uicrIvZQ=6582897f26826ac94e302ab3b89c132f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yqqlm.com%2Findex%2Findex%2FgetInterUrl%3FuicrIvZQ%3D6582897f26826ac94e302ab3b89c132f&h=c1accdc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"505de2bfdfca0c98ecb1ba15be5d178ed5bc8dbb","tid":2354643,"uid":185656,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"佢算top5謙虛"},{"pid":"b1c8685063ef9b62bae46a98324173f599ec6695","tid":2354643,"uid":30464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e35bb26c9eef1608c54ffd1ad109f2243e87f36","tid":2354643,"uid":67225,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.yqqlm.com/index/index/getInterUrl?uicrIvZQ=6582897f26826ac94e302ab3b89c132f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yqqlm.com%2Findex%2Findex%2FgetInterUrl%3FuicrIvZQ%3D6582897f26826ac94e302ab3b89c132f&h=c1accdc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"世界級"},{"pid":"2de5d089532b6e3f4c854dee90a21cf857413233","tid":2354643,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"贏身體質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炒6-2 果球 後防拉都拉佢唔住 <br />\n但問教練鐘意邊d一定揀kane"},{"pid":"4badc5bb89a59b002aa8ef4b122d1278616b8b2f","tid":2354643,"uid":83172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"賣笑型前鋒top5"},{"pid":"eb509c13dc7107880133b662696d1d6d69c1a6d6","tid":2354643,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2de5d089532b6e3f4c854dee90a21cf857413233","tid":2354643,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"贏身體質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炒6-2 果球 後防拉都拉佢唔住 <br />\n但問教練鐘意邊d一定揀kane"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"控球能力佢同Kane差9條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b335827105a20c62bf6fa5c21adccd72b9847fb1","tid":2354643,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"不如練好啲控波先啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715574b94d8966bcd85d78c991ae2dfd9051334d","tid":2354643,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote